headline.main: Whitecaps, Union Settle for 0-0 Draw in MLS Opener
headline.print_headline: Whitecaps, Union Settle for 0-0 Draw in MLS Opener

lead_paragraph: The Vancouver Whitecaps and Philadelphia Union settled for a 0-0 draw Sunday night in the Major League Soccer opener for both teams.
